XXIO Mens XXIO8 Golf Hybrids

Faster swinging for longer distance, even with a heavier head!

The XXIO series, a popular favorite among a wide range of golfers, has been number one in annual sales 1 for 14 consecutive years in Japan since it first debuted. Meanwhile, Sakura Yokomine, Inbee Park, and other professional golfers have scored numerous tour victories playing with XXIO clubs. In order to respond to golfers' demand for a club that is easier swinging and longer hitting, the new XXIO8 follows an all-new design approach focusing on swing moment of inertia (MOI) to achieve a significant flight distance increase.

XXIO Mens XXIO8 Hybrids feature:

  • Woods: #3H • #4H • #5H.
  • Lofts: 19.0 • 21.0 • 23.0.
  • Dual Speed Technology maximizes the power of the golfer's swing to achieve higher clubhead speed and higher ball speed.
  • Heavier clubhead increases kinetic energy at impact for more distance.
  • Face thickness individually designed for each club number.
  • The new face thickness design is individually customized for each loft to match the golfer's strike point.
  • Extending the thin portion to the upper toe and lower heel areas creates a larger sweet spot and higher ball speed.
  • Same graphite shaft as the driver to achieve higher head speed, even with a heavier club head.
  • XXIO MP800 graphite shaft available in Regular • Stiff.
  • Available in right- and left-hand.
  • Includes headcover.
  • Authorized XXIO Retailer.
  • Click Detail Views & Info under the image above for alternate views and more details.

XXIO Hybrids... Great Clubs Made Even Better!
